*cfn-lint version: 0.29.5*

cfn-lint incorrectly raises the use of `dotnetcore3.1` as an error.

Support for the value is declared in the CFN reference:

https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSCloudFormation/latest/UserGuide/aws-resource-lambda-function.html

The following example will raise the error on validation.

```json
{
  "Description": "Name lambda functions",
  "Resources": {
    "LambdaFunctionName": {
      "Type": "AWS::Lambda::Function",
      "Properties": {
        "Runtime": "dotnetcore3.1",
        "Description": "Description",
        "Timeout": 60,
        "Code": {
          "S3Key": "Name.zip",
          "S3Bucket": {
            "Fn::ImportValue": "bucketID"
          }
        },
        "FunctionName": "ADSConditionalForwarder",
        "Handler": "Handler",
        "Role": {
          "Ref": "IamRole"
        },
        "VpcConfig": {
          "SubnetIds": [
            {
              "Fn::ImportValue": "subnet1"
            },
            {
              "Fn::ImportValue": "subnet2"
            },
            {
              "Fn::ImportValue": "subnet3"
            }
          ],
          "SecurityGroupIds": {
            "Ref": "SecurityGroup"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

*cfn-lint version: (0.29.2)*

*Description of issue.*

Hi.  I'm trying to write a custom rule that will evaluate IAM policies.  I'm at a point where I'm trying to evaluate an IAM policy statement.  Something like:

    {
        "Effect": "Allow",
        "Action": [
            "cloudformation:DescribeStacks"
        ],
        "Resource": [
            {
                "Fn::Sub": "${AWS::StackId}"
            }
        ]
    }

The variables could be either CF template pseudo-variables, like `${AWS::Region}`,  intrinsic functions like `{"Fn::Sub": "..."}` `{ "Fn::GetAtt": "..."}`, `{"Fn::ImportValue": "..."}`, `{"Ref": "..."}`, etc...

Is there anything in the cfn-lint library that will interpolate values like this and provide the result?
